  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The overall purpose of this research is to learn how Parkinson's disease affects thinking and
      memory in everyday life. Participation will involve thinking tests, questionnaires and
      interviews about thinking and activities in everyday life.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
